"and Keep Working:
Everything You Need to Know

20:34.934 --> 20:36.669
to Stay Productive and Alive,"

20:36.703 --> 20:38.371
you'll notice
in the left column,

20:38.405 --> 20:40.973
filing for time off,
that is strongly discouraged.

20:41.007 --> 20:44.043
We feel that if you just
rest up over the weekend,

20:44.076 --> 20:45.812
you'll be good to go
on Monday.

20:45.845 --> 20:48.415
I would, however, like
to go over some of the symptoms

20:48.448 --> 20:50.583
you may encounter with ILD.

20:50.617 --> 20:51.918
For starters,
you may experience

20:51.951 --> 20:54.387
loose or bloody stools.
